TimGrandfather (Default): Tim...
TimGrandfather: I have to tell you something...
Tim: What do you mean grandfather?
TimGrandfather: Your father is missing.
TimGrandfather: We haven't received a signal from your father for almost a week. We have to hope that he is doing well.
Tim: How terrifying, what can we do?
